{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"37983a23a8","title":"在接见汇报卫生工作同志时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a5515bdd8","index":0,"year":1965,"month":8,"day":2,"articleId":"37983a23a8"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"8490037019","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"钱信忠（1911-—2009），江苏宝山（今属上海）人，当时任中华人民共和国卫生部部长。张凯（1912-1996），湖南浏阳人，当时任卫生部副部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d4d211809b","type":"title","text":"在接见汇报卫生工作同志时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"8490037019","type":"paragraph","text":"情况）（八月二日，钱信惠和张凯“向毛泽东汇报了卫生工作的相关","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"cccb14a493","type":"paragraph","text":"钱信忠、张凯（以下简称钱、张）：主席对卫生工作的指示和批评很中肯，是完全正确的，我们根据主席指示作了检查，请主席再给我们一些指示。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"9c986b88df","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：我要讲的都已讲了。你们打算怎么办？","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"c515dad97f","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：近来我们根据主席和中央的指示进行了讨论，打算组织城币卫生人员下去做几件事情。第一件，除给农民治病外，就是为农村生产队培训不脱产卫生员。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"46feefa5ab","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：训练多长时间","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"e6f2cef731","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：半个月左右。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"9d1e8134f4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：半个月太短了吧","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"af16b71456","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：他们主要学会些针炎，常见病的治疗和一些预防工作，训练后还要带他们做","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"43cee61ffc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：带很重要，带多长时间","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"5b2f06b741","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：城市医疗队下去可一直带，共带三四个月。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"9bfe834084","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这还可以，带三四个月，学会治十几种病。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"20b7204188","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到搞一些半农半读训练班时）","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"761c62ee44","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：我们还在农村搞了一些半农半读训练班。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"adef7493de","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：半农半读怎么搞的？","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"777fcf14db","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：采取农忙不学，农闲多学的方式。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"3a6bcabd68","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：多长时间","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"12f1bb61a6","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：二年，三年。","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"4bf0a222ab","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：二年就是读一年书，三年就是读一年半书，这个办法好。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"c8806be160","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到根据中央、主席指示作了检查时）","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"3f2a4849fb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：现在有多少卫生技术人员？","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"b221ba856e","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：共有一百四十多万卫生技术人员，其中公社和医生联合集体办的六十万，拿国家工资的八十多万。","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"a812d9a20d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这个队伍不小！","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"1af0e71826","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：主席批评我们只为城市人口服务，很对，现在高级医务人员百分之八十在城市，其中百分之七十在大城市，百分之二十在县城，只有百分之十在农村。经费，包括县在内农村占百分之二十五，百分之七十五用在城市。","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"7a13b9610e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们用了这么多人力，这么多钱，为那么少的人服务。","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"aacebeac1c","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：主席指示后我们才清醒了。","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"1f401a10e3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们研究过神医没有","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"d7b21ea477","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：我们没有研究过。","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"8ab5cde967","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：神医有三个好处：神药它保险，不会害人，没有毒；第二个好处是省钱，几个铜板就可以了；第三是给病人精神的安感，病也就好了。","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"21441cd198","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：许多病不治也可以好。","index":29,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"13b0e21543","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：比骗人的医生要好。","index":30,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"f1ea43b231","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：通过四清和医疗队下乡，了解到农村卫生队伍很复杂。","index":31,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"6cfc2c4616","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么复杂？","index":32,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"6c627f301e","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：有许多人过去不是医生，看些医书就加入医务人员队伍里来了。","index":33,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"1743e46523","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：看些什么书","index":34,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"56e975ff94","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：看些中医书，看些药方。农村医务队伍中，政治情况复杂、技术水平低的占百分之四十左右。","index":35,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"d843dd2f3e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：环人不多吧！","index":36,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"beba762f7d","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：真正坏人占百分之五左右，但政治技术水平低的较多，占百分之四十左右，这个队伍如果没有新生的力量，取消他们还不容易。","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"311687d33a","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：现在正在召开医学教育会议，讨论主席、总理指示，要办三年制卫生学校，为农村培养医生。","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"ab30ebc28e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：高等教育要学五年，读那么长时间书，值得研究。","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"1238a1bae3","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：现在想两条腿走路，办三年制，多在农村办，在农村招生。","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"e59020864f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：招什么生？","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"0d662b05da","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：大部分招高中生","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"6a4b546b50","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：初中还不行吗","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"40665d4877","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：目前农村高中生还不少","index":44,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"7d28fc1533","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：招中学生还不行吗？你们不在城市招了吗？","index":45,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"0f597f05fd","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：城市也招一些，主要在农村招。我们体会，主席认为读五年书时间太长，至于招生不一定强调高中生。","index":46,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"9f99120fb6","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：医生的政治思想重要，只有技术没有政治不行。","index":47,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"265213fa08","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这一点很重要。医生一定要政治好，招些政治好的中学生就可以了。","index":48,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"754e0a5abb","type":"paragraph","text":"（钱忠信、张凯又汇报了城市问题","index":49,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"13123b5ca2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们对城市是不是服务得好","index":50,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"c822045780","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：也没有服务好，要求愈来愈高。","index":51,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"fa1a7ad22f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么愈来愈高？","index":52,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"3c38dfd51e","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：以北京来讲，五十多万干部公费医疗，八十多万工人劳保，还有家属。","index":53,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"692cf2cc17","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：工人不是“老爷”，工人还是要为他们服务的","index":54,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"d3dc3ab847","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：工厂医务工作没有搞好，工人也都到医院去看病。","index":55,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"b16735d49c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们为什么不在工厂设不脱产卫生员呢？小厂可以设卫生员，大厂设医务所。","index":56,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"b1b477a69e","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：非正式医生开不了假条，要请假还要到医院去，经医生开证明才行。","index":57,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"2e0971bb21","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这涉及劳保问题，要好好考虑。","index":58,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"54520e8784","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：城市医院压力大，公费医疗包下来，一个钱不出，到处看病。","index":59,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"84815d6c66","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：看了病，拿了药，还不吃。","index":60,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"c44a357b37","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：刘主席、总理指示城市要组织医务人员下农村的问题，每年下去三分之一。","index":61,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"1b831ba2ac","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么下去？多久？","index":62,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"004769af67","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：轮流下去。下去后城市医疗卫生工作仍较重。我们打算高等医学院校学生三年后就一边工作一边上课。护士也一面工作一面学习。","index":63,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"b6732637ab","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：光会念书是不行的","index":64,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"d738f24b5d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们对打仗考虑了没有","index":65,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"addd5232e4","type":"paragraph","text":"答：中央指示后考虑了。","index":66,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"3f19df6d10","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么考虑的","index":67,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"a6c3a1de25","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：组织了几十个医疗队，随时准备赴前线服务。现在的医院对战争没有训练。组织医疗队训练，有的地方已开始了。","index":68,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"332cee3036","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：打仗了还能都到北京医院看病？要考虑到打仗。你们分科那么细，打起仗来怎么办？打起仗来还不是什么都要看，只会内科不会外科怎么行！","index":69,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"668af4dd92","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：过去部队青年人多，疑难病可能不多，有的也许不认识，但医学科学是发展的，要有一小部分力量搞尖端。","index":70,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"0007dc8d1c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：搞科研的人看不看病","index":71,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"fd5a9c11f4","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：一部分人看病，一部分人不看病。","index":72,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"b1f370169a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：什么人不看病？","index":73,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"a7bcf5b5c4","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：搞基础学科的，如搞生理、药理、生化的，研究理论不看病。","index":74,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"ce6d70af38","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：理论还是要结合实际啊！","index":75,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"57cc2e9903","type":"paragraph","text":"钱、张：定一同志说百分之五搞尖端就可以了，现在共有科研队伍一万人，其中技术队伍五千人","index":76,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"f4148a38a3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：科学尖端还是要搞的","index":77,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"c22a7a1614","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到各级党委应当多抓卫生工作时）","index":78,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"79001f886d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这话很对，党委是集体领导，什么都要管。卫生部门是为人民服务的，当然要抓，党委也要研究卫生工作。","index":79,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"732268bf08","type":"paragraph","text":"（钱忠信、张凯又请示农村卫生员工分问题。人民公社六十条规定，补贴工分不超过百分之二。卫生员的补贴工分社员同意给，但六十条没有规定。）","index":80,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"6cd73600c8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：给群众办好事，没有问题，农民会同意的。现在干部参加了劳动，百分之二已用不了，有的地方只用百分之一，工分不成问题，农民会同意的。","index":81,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"d0ff544e08","type":"paragraph","text":"（钱忠信、张凯又请示主席，建议中央今年召开一次农村卫生工作会议，中央召开，可以找省、市领导同志参加）","index":82,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"3ce61be55c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：可以。","index":83,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"550f3fd4b6","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到药品问题时","index":84,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"020f12330b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：药品应当降价。","index":85,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"7f4ddabd05","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：天津计划生育不要钱。看来国家出了钱，实际是划得来的。国家出点钱保护生产力是合算的。药钱拿不起也可以不拿。你们开展农村卫生工作后，要搞节制生育","index":86,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"0bcf760955","type":"paragraph","text":"（最后，钱忠信、张凯请示主席还有什么指示）","index":87,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"},{"id":"44470f732c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：没有什么了，就按你们讲的办吧","index":88,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8"}],"page":{"id":"cd883937b9","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"37983a23a8","start":136,"end":141}}}},"__N_SSG":true}